reviewText: Like another review I've read.........I believe the guy's "story" and that he really had these NDE experiences as he relates them in the DVD. However, its a little "wishy washy" in the way he relates it. Interesting story, but watching it once was enough for me.
I believe that this guys experience was genuine... But.. He did seem to waffle on alot in a "hairy fairy" kind of a way. It was ok and his encounter was interesting but I couldn't watch it again.
